{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775891358735,"sessionID":"ses_284a3f4d3ffe8bFOTfB7U7JhyS","part":{"id":"prt_d7b5cd3ca001laRAjDosFVf15R","messageID":"msg_d7b5cc067001TUEsZVyR4L8MtB","sessionID":"ses_284a3f4d3ffe8bFOTfB7U7JhyS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_a463d7188f5f4555b9f43f45","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md","content":"# AR-041: E2E 集成测试\n\n## 1. Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目构建全面的端到端（E2E）集成测试框架，验证整个系统从 Kubernetes CRD 创建到代码执行、Agent 调用的完整链路。\n\n本提案针对 AR-041 需求，基于现有的 `test/e2e/` 测试基础设施，扩展以下核心测试场景：\n\n1. **AgentRuntime 生命周期管理** - 验证 AgentRuntime CRD 的创建、更新、删除及状态同步\n2. **CodeInterpreter 执行流程** - 验证代码解释器的完整执行链路（提交 → 调度 → 执行 → 结果返回）\n3. **Warm Pool 机制验证** - 验证 CodeInterpreter 暖池的预创建、复用和回收\n4. **Router 路由和会话管理** - 验证请求路由、会话绑定、JWT 认证和 Token 管理\n5. **多组件集成交互** - 验证 Workload Manager、Router、Sandbox、PicoD 之间的协作\n\n本 E2E 测试框架使用生成的 `client-go` 库与 Kubernetes API 交互，确保测试与生产环境行为一致。\n\n## 2. Scope\n\n**Module:** `test/e2e`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** L\n\n### 2.1 In Scope\n\n| 测试类别 | 测试文件 | 优先级 | 测试类型 | 依赖 |\n|----------|----------|--------|----------|------|\n| **AgentRuntime E2E** | | | | |\n| AgentRuntime 创建和暴露 | `agentruntime_test.go` | P0 | E2E | client-go |\n| AgentRuntime 状态同步 | `agentruntime_status_test.go` | P0 | E2E | client-go, informer |\n| AgentRuntime 更新和删除 | `agentruntime_lifecycle_test.go` | P1 | E2E | client-go |\n| AgentRuntime 标签路由 | `agentruntime_routing_test.go` | P1 | E2E | Router API |\n| **CodeInterpreter E2E** | | | | |\n| CodeInterpreter 创建 | `codeinterpreter_test.go` | P0 | E2E | client-go |\n| 代码执行完整流程 | `codeinterpreter_execution_test.go` | P0 | E2E | Router API, PicoD |\n| CodeInterpreter 状态机 | `codeinterpreter_status_test.go` | P1 | E2E | client-go |\n| Warm Pool 机制 | `codeinterpreter_warmpool_test.go` | P1 | E2E | client-go, Workload Manager API |\n| 资源限制执行 | `codeinterpreter_limits_test.go` | P1 | E2E | PicoD API |\n| **Router E2E** | | | | |\n| Router 健康检查 | `router_health_test.go` | P0 | E2E | Router API |\n| Invoke 接口测试 | `router_invoke_test.go` | P0 | E2E | Router API |\n| 会话管理 | `router_session_test.go` | P1 | E2E | Router API, Redis |\n| JWT 认证和 Token 管理 | `router_auth_test.go` | P1 | E2E | Router API |\n| **集成场景** | | | | |\n| 多租户隔离 | `multi_tenant_test.go` | P2 | E2E | Namespace, RBAC |\n| 故障恢复 | `failure_recovery_test.go` | P2 | E2E | Chaos Engineering |\n| 并发和压力 | `concurrency_test.go` | P2 | 负载测试 | Locust/vegeta |\n\n### 2.2 Out of Scope\n\n- 单元测试（由 `pkg/*/` 下的单元测试覆盖）\n- 集成测试（由 `test/integration/` 覆盖组件间集成）\n- 性能基准测试（由单独的性能测试计划覆盖）\n- 安全渗透测试（由安全审计计划覆盖）\n- PicoD 内部实现细节测试（由 `pkg/picod/` 单元测试覆盖）\n\n## 3. Current State Analysis\n\n### 3.1 现有 E2E 测试基础设施\n\n当前 `test/e2e/` 目录包含：\n\n1. **Go E2E 测试** (`e2e_test.go`):\n   - `TestHealthCheck`: Workload Manager 健康检查\n   - `TestRouterHealth`: Router 健康检查\n   - `TestInvokeEchoAgent`: 调用 Echo Agent\n   - `TestCodeInterpreter`: 代码解释器执行\n\n2. **Python E2E 测试** (`test_codeinterpreter.py`):\n   - 使用 Python SDK 进行代码执行测试\n\n3. **测试脚本** (`run_e2e.sh`):\n   - Kind 集群创建和管理\n   - agent-sandbox CRD 安装\n   - 本地 Docker 镜像构建和加载\n   - Helm 安装 AgentCube\n   - E2E fixtures 应用\n   - 端口转发和 Token 生成\n   - 失败时日志收集\n\n4. **Fixtures**:\n   - `echo_agent.yaml`: Echo Agent 定义\n   - `e2e_code_interpreter.yaml`: CodeInterpreter 资源\n   - `e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml`: 带暖池的 CodeInterpreter\n\n### 3.2 Gaps Identified\n\n1. **Kubernetes API 直接测试缺失** - 当前测试仅通过 HTTP API 验证，未使用 client-go 直接操作 CRD\n2. **状态机验证不完整** - 未验证 CRD 状态转换（Pending → Running → Succeeded/Failed）\n3. **Warm Pool 未测试** - 暖池机制的预创建、复用和回收逻辑未覆盖\n4. **会话管理测试缺失** - Router 会话绑定、过期清理未测试\n5. **JWT 认证流程未覆盖** - Token 生成、刷新、撤销未测试\n6. **故障场景缺失** - 无 Pod 失败、网络分区、资源不足等场景测试\n7. **多租户场景未验证** - Namespace 隔离、RBAC 权限未测试\n\n### 3.3 Client-Go 基础设施\n\n根据 `deployment/client-go.md`，已生成完整的 Kubernetes client-go 库：\n\n```go\n// Clientset 使用示例\nconfig, _ := rest.InClusterConfig()\nclientset, _ := clientset.NewForConfig(config)\n\n// 获取 AgentRuntime\nruntimeV1alpha1 := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1()\nagentRuntimes := runtimeV1alpha1.AgentRuntimes(namespace)\nar, _ := agentRuntimes.Get(ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n\n// 创建 CodeInterpreter\nci := &runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{...}\nresult, _ := runtimeV1alpha1.CodeInterpreters(namespace).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n\n// Watch 资源变化\nwatcher, _ := agentRuntimes.Watch(ctx, metav1.ListOptions{})\nfor event := range watcher.ResultChan() {\n    // 处理事件\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 Informer 机制\n\n```go\n// SharedInformerFactory 使用\nfactory := externalversions.NewSharedInformerFactory(clientset, 30*time.Second)\ninformer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()\n\n// 添加事件处理器\ninformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n    AddFunc:    func(obj interface{}) { /* ... */ },\n    UpdateFunc: func(oldObj, newObj interface{}) { /* ... */ },\n    DeleteFunc: func(obj interface{}) { /* ... */ },\n})\n\n// 启动 Informer\nfactory.Start(stopCh)\nfactory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)\n```\n\n## 4. Proposed Changes\n\n### 4.1 测试框架结构\n\n```\ntest/e2e/\n├── framework/\n│   ├── client.go              # Client-go 封装和测试辅助\n│   ├── cluster.go             # Kind 集群管理\n│   ├── fixtures.go            # Test fixtures 创建和管理\n│   ├── wait.go                # 等待条件满足的工具\n│   └── cleanup.go             # 资源清理\n├── agents/\n│   ├── agentruntime_test.go\n│   ├── agentruntime_status_test.go\n│   └── agentruntime_lifecycle_test.go\n├── code_interpreter/\n│   ├── codeinterpreter_test.go\n│   ├── codeinterpreter_execution_test.go\n│   ├── codeinterpreter_status_test.go\n│   ├── codeinterpreter_warmpool_test.go\n│   └── codeinterpreter_limits_test.go\n├── router/\n│   ├── router_health_test.go\n│   ├── router_invoke_test.go\n│   ├── router_session_test.go\n│   └── router_auth_test.go\n├── integration/\n│   ├── multi_tenant_test.go\n│   ├── failure_recovery_test.go\n│   └── concurrency_test.go\n├── fixtures/\n│   ├── echo_agent.yaml\n│   ├── agentruntime.yaml\n│   ├── codeinterpreter.yaml\n│   └── codeinterpreter_warmpool.yaml\n├── e2e_test.go                # 现有测试\n├── run_e2e.sh                 # 现有脚本\n└── README.md                  # 更新文档\n```\n\n### 4.2 核心测试框架 (`framework/`)\n\n#### 4.2.1 Client-go 封装 (`framework/client.go`)\n\n```go\n// E2EClient provides a high-level interface for E2E testing\ntype E2EClient struct {\n    kubeClient     kubernetes.Interface\n    runtimeClient  clientset.Interface\n    restConfig     *rest.Config\n    namespace      string\n    httpClient     *http.Client\n    routerURL      string\n    workloadMgrURL string\n    apiToken       string\n}\n\n// NewE2EClient creates a new E2E client\nfunc NewE2EClient(namespace string) (*E2EClient, error)\n\n// KubeClient returns the Kubernetes clientset\nfunc (c *E2EClient) KubeClient() kubernetes.Interface\n\n// RuntimeClient returns the AgentCube runtime clientset\nfunc (c *E2EClient) RuntimeClient() clientset.Interface\n\n// CreateAgentRuntime creates an AgentRuntime resource\nfunc (c *E2EClient) CreateAgentRuntime(ctx context.Context, ar *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime) error\n\n// WaitForAgentRuntimeReady waits for AgentRuntime to be ready\nfunc (c *E2EClient) WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx context.Context, name string, timeout time.Duration) error\n\n// CreateCodeInterpreter creates a CodeInterpreter resource\nfunc (c *E2EClient) CreateCodeInterpreter(ctx context.Context, ci *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) error\n\n// WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase waits for CodeInterpreter to reach a phase\nfunc (c *E2EClient) WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx context.Context, name string, phase runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterPhase, timeout time.Duration) error\n```\n\n#### 4.2.2 等待工具 (`framework/wait.go`)\n\n```go\n// WaitForCondition waits for a condition to be true\nfunc WaitForCondition(ctx context.Context, name string, timeout time.Duration, condition func() (bool, error)) error\n\n// WaitForAgentRuntimeReady waits for AgentRuntime status.ready = true\nfunc WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx context.Context, client clientset.Interface, namespace, name string, timeout time.Duration) error\n\n// WaitForCodeInterpreterRunning waits for CodeInterpreter phase = Running\nfunc WaitForCodeInterpreterRunning(ctx context.Context, client clientset.Interface, namespace, name string, timeout time.Duration) error\n\n// WaitForRouterHealth waits for Router health endpoint to return OK\nfunc WaitForRouterHealth(ctx context.Context, routerURL string, timeout time.Duration) error\n```\n\n#### 4.2.3 Fixtures 管理 (`framework/fixtures.go`)\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeFixtures provides helper methods to create AgentRuntime resources\ntype AgentRuntimeFixtures struct{}\n\nfunc (f *AgentRuntimeFixtures) NewEchoAgent(name, namespace string) *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\nfunc (f *AgentRuntimeFixtures) NewAgentWithBackendURL(name, namespace, backendURL string) *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\nfunc (f *AgentRuntimeFixtures) NewAgentWithLabels(name, namespace string, labels map[string]string) *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\n\n// CodeInterpreterFixtures provides helper methods to create CodeInterpreter resources\ntype CodeInterpreterFixtures struct{}\n\nfunc (f *CodeInterpreterFixtures) NewBasic(name, namespace string) *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\nfunc (f *CodeInterpreterFixtures) NewWithWarmPool(name, namespace string, minIdle, maxIdle int) *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\nfunc (f *CodeInterpreterFixtures) NewWithResourceLimits(name, namespace string, cpu, memory string) *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\n```\n\n### 4.3 AgentRuntime E2E 测试\n\n#### 4.3.1 创建和暴露测试 (`agents/agentruntime_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestAgentRuntimeCreation tests basic AgentRuntime creation\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeCreation(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &AgentRuntimeFixtures{}\n    \n    ar := fixture.NewEchoAgent(\"test-echo-agent\", client.Namespace())\n    \n    // Create\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    created, err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    require.NotNil(t, created)\n    \n    // Wait for ready\n    err = client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, created.Name, 2*time.Minute)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Verify status\n    status, err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Get(ctx, created.Name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.True(t, status.Status.Ready)\n    assert.NotNil(t, status.Status.BackendURL)\n}\n\n// TestAgentRuntimeWithLabelExposure tests exposure via label\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeWithLabelExposure(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &AgentRuntimeFixtures{}\n    \n    labels := map[string]string{\n        \"agentcube/expose\": \"true\",\n    }\n    ar := fixture.NewAgentWithLabels(\"test-exposed-agent\", client.Namespace(), labels)\n    \n    // Create and wait\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, created.Name, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Verify Router can route to this agent\n    resp, err := client.InvokeAgent(ctx, created.Name, map[string]interface{}{\"message\": \"hello\"})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, resp.StatusCode)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.3.2 状态同步测试 (`agents/agentruntime_status_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestAgentRuntimeStatusSync tests status synchronization between pod and CRD\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeStatusSync(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &AgentRuntimeFixtures{}\n    \n    ar := fixture.NewEchoAgent(\"test-status-sync\", client.Namespace())\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    \n    // Watch status changes\n    watcher, err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Watch(ctx, metav1.SingleObject(created.ObjectMeta))\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    defer watcher.Stop()\n    \n    // Collect status updates\n    statusUpdates := []runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeStatus{}\n    timeout := time.After(3 * time.Minute)\n    \n    for {\n        select {\n        case event, ok := <-watcher.ResultChan():\n            if !ok {\n                break\n            }\n            if ar, ok := event.Object.(*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime); ok {\n                statusUpdates = append(statusUpdates, ar.Status)\n                if ar.Status.Ready {\n                    goto done\n                }\n            }\n        case <-timeout:\n            t.Fatal(\"Timeout waiting for AgentRuntime to be ready\")\n        }\n    }\ndone:\n    // Verify status progression\n    assert.GreaterOrEqual(t, len(statusUpdates), 1)\n    assert.True(t, statusUpdates[len(statusUpdates)-1].Ready)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.3.3 生命周期测试 (`agents/agentruntime_lifecycle_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestAgentRuntimeUpdate tests updating an AgentRuntime\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeUpdate(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &AgentRuntimeFixtures{}\n    \n    ar := fixture.NewEchoAgent(\"test-update\", client.Namespace())\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, created.Name, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Update\n    created.Spec.SessionTimeout = \"10m\"\n    updated, err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Update(ctx, created, metav1.UpdateOptions{})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"10m\", updated.Spec.SessionTimeout)\n}\n\n// TestAgentRuntimeDelete tests deletion and cleanup\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeDelete(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &AgentRuntimeFixtures{}\n    \n    ar := fixture.NewEchoAgent(\"test-delete\", client.Namespace())\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, created.Name, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Delete\n    err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        AgentRuntimes(client.Namespace()).Delete(ctx, created.Name, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Wait for deletion\n    err = client.WaitForResourceDeleted(ctx, \"agentruntime\", created.Name, 1*time.Minute)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n}\n```\n\n### 4.4 CodeInterpreter E2E 测试\n\n#### 4.4.1 执行流程测试 (`code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_execution_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestCodeInterpreterExecution tests full code execution flow\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterExecution(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &CodeInterpreterFixtures{}\n    \n    ci := fixture.NewBasic(\"test-execution\", client.Namespace())\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, err := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Wait for Running\n    err = client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name, \n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterRunning, 2*time.Minute)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Invoke via Router\n    payload := map[string]string{\n        \"code\": \"print('Hello from CodeInterpreter')\",\n    }\n    resp, err := client.InvokeCodeInterpreter(ctx, created.Name, payload)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, resp.StatusCode)\n    \n    // Verify output\n    var result map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp.Body).Decode(&result)\n    assert.Contains(t, result[\"stdout\"].(string), \"Hello from CodeInterpreter\")\n    \n    // Wait for Succeeded\n    err = client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name,\n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSucceeded, 1*time.Minute)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.4.2 Warm Pool 测试 (`code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_warmpool_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestWarmPoolPreCreation tests warm pool pre-creation\nfunc TestWarmPoolPreCreation(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &CodeInterpreterFixtures{}\n    \n    minIdle := 2\n    maxIdle := 5\n    ci := fixture.NewWithWarmPool(\"test-warmpool\", client.Namespace(), minIdle, maxIdle)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    \n    // Wait for Running\n    client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name,\n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterRunning, 3*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Verify warm pool size\n    status, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Get(ctx, created.Name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n    \n    assert.Equal(t, minIdle, status.Status.WarmPool.IdleCount)\n    assert.GreaterOrEqual(t, status.Status.WarmPool.TotalCount, minIdle)\n}\n\n// TestWarmPoolReuse tests sandbox reuse from warm pool\nfunc TestWarmPoolReuse(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &CodeInterpreterFixtures{}\n    \n    ci := fixture.NewWithWarmPool(\"test-reuse\", client.Namespace(), 1, 2)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name,\n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterRunning, 3*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Execute multiple times\n    sandboxIDs := make(map[string]bool)\n    for i := 0; i < 3; i++ {\n        resp, _ := client.InvokeCodeInterpreter(ctx, created.Name, \n            map[string]string{\"code\": \"import os; print(os.getpid())\"})\n        \n        var result map[string]interface{}\n        json.NewDecoder(resp.Body).Decode(&result)\n        \n        // Extract sandbox ID from output\n        sandboxIDs[extractSandboxID(result)] = true\n    }\n    \n    // Verify some reuse occurred (fewer unique sandboxes than invocations)\n    assert.Less(t, len(sandboxIDs), 3)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.4.3 资源限制测试 (`code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_limits_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestResourceLimitTimeout tests command timeout enforcement\nfunc TestResourceLimitTimeout(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &CodeInterpreterFixtures{}\n    \n    ci := fixture.NewWithResourceLimits(\"test-timeout\", client.Namespace(), \"0.5\", \"128Mi\")\n    ci.Spec.Timeout = \"5s\"\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name,\n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterRunning, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Execute long-running command\n    resp, _ := client.InvokeCodeInterpreter(ctx, created.Name,\n        map[string]string{\"code\": \"import time; time.sleep(10)\"})\n    \n    var result map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp.Body).Decode(&result)\n    \n    assert.Equal(t, \"timeout\", result[\"error_type\"])\n}\n\n// TestResourceLimitMemory tests memory limit enforcement\nfunc TestResourceLimitMemory(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    fixture := &CodeInterpreterFixtures{}\n    \n    ci := fixture.NewWithResourceLimits(\"test-oom\", client.Namespace(), \"0.5\", \"64Mi\")\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create\n    created, _ := client.RuntimeClient().RuntimeV1alpha1().\n        CodeInterpreters(client.Namespace()).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    client.WaitForCodeInterpreterPhase(ctx, created.Name,\n        runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterRunning, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Execute memory-heavy command\n    resp, _ := client.InvokeCodeInterpreter(ctx, created.Name,\n        map[string]string{\"code\": \"data = b'x' * 100000000\"})\n    \n    var result map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp.Body).Decode(&result)\n    \n    assert.Equal(t, \"oom\", result[\"error_type\"])\n}\n```\n\n### 4.5 Router E2E 测试\n\n#### 4.5.1 会话管理测试 (`router/router_session_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestSessionBinding tests session binding to sandbox\nfunc TestSessionBinding(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // First invocation creates session\n    payload := map[string]string{\"message\": \"first\"}\n    resp1, _ := client.InvokeAgent(ctx, \"echo-agent\", payload)\n    \n    var result1 map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp1.Body).Decode(&result1)\n    sessionID1 := result1[\"session_id\"].(string)\n    \n    // Second invocation with same session should reuse sandbox\n    resp2, _ := client.InvokeAgentWithSession(ctx, \"echo-agent\", sessionID1, payload)\n    \n    var result2 map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp2.Body).Decode(&result2)\n    sandboxID1 := result1[\"sandbox_id\"].(string)\n    sandboxID2 := result2[\"sandbox_id\"].(string)\n    \n    assert.Equal(t, sandboxID1, sandboxID2)\n}\n\n// TestSessionTimeout tests session expiration\nfunc TestSessionTimeout(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Invoke with short TTL agent\n    payload := map[string]string{\"message\": \"hello\"}\n    resp, _ := client.InvokeAgent(ctx, \"echo-agent-short-ttl\", payload)\n    \n    var result map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp.Body).Decode(&result)\n    sessionID := result[\"session_id\"].(string)\n    \n    // Wait for session to expire\n    time.Sleep(35 * time.Second)\n    \n    // Invoke again should create new session\n    resp2, _ := client.InvokeAgent(ctx, \"echo-agent-short-ttl\", payload)\n    var result2 map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(resp2.Body).Decode(&result2)\n    sessionID2 := result2[\"session_id\"].(string)\n    \n    assert.NotEqual(t, sessionID, sessionID2)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.5.2 认证测试 (`router/router_auth_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestJWTTokenGeneration tests token generation via API\nfunc TestJWTTokenGeneration(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Generate token\n    tokenResp, err := client.GenerateToken(ctx, \"test-user\", []string{\"agent:invoke\"})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    var tokenResult map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(tokenResp.Body).Decode(&tokenResult)\n    token := tokenResult[\"token\"].(string)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, token)\n    \n    // Use token for invocation\n    resp, err := client.InvokeAgentWithToken(ctx, \"echo-agent\", token, \n        map[string]string{\"message\": \"hello\"})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, resp.StatusCode)\n}\n\n// TestTokenRefresh tests token refresh flow\nfunc TestTokenRefresh(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Generate initial token\n    tokenResp, _ := client.GenerateToken(ctx, \"test-user\", []string{\"agent:invoke\"})\n    var tokenResult map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(tokenResp.Body).Decode(&tokenResult)\n    refreshToken := tokenResult[\"refresh_token\"].(string)\n    \n    // Refresh token\n    refreshResp, err := client.RefreshToken(ctx, refreshToken)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    var refreshResult map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(refreshResp.Body).Decode(&refreshResult)\n    newToken := refreshResult[\"token\"].(string)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, newToken)\n    assert.NotEqual(t, tokenResult[\"token\"], newToken)\n}\n\n// TestTokenRevoke tests token revocation\nfunc TestTokenRevoke(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Generate token\n    tokenResp, _ := client.GenerateToken(ctx, \"test-user\", []string{\"agent:invoke\"})\n    var tokenResult map[string]interface{}\n    json.NewDecoder(tokenResp.Body).Decode(&tokenResult)\n    token := tokenResult[\"token\"].(string)\n    \n    // Revoke token\n    err := client.RevokeToken(ctx, token)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Try to use revoked token\n    resp, _ := client.InvokeAgentWithToken(ctx, \"echo-agent\", token,\n        map[string]string{\"message\": \"hello\"})\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusUnauthorized, resp.StatusCode)\n}\n```\n\n### 4.6 集成场景测试\n\n#### 4.6.1 多租户隔离 (`integration/multi_tenant_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestNamespaceIsolation tests multi-namespace isolation\nfunc TestNamespaceIsolation(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create resources in namespace A\n    nsA := \"e2e-test-namespace-a\"\n    client.CreateNamespace(ctx, nsA)\n    arA := createAgentInNamespace(client, nsA, \"agent-a\")\n    \n    // Create resources in namespace B\n    nsB := \"e2e-test-namespace-b\"\n    client.CreateNamespace(ctx, nsB)\n    arB := createAgentInNamespace(client, nsB, \"agent-b\")\n    \n    // Verify service account in A cannot access B\n    tokenA := createSAToken(client, nsA, \"test-sa\")\n    resp, _ := client.GetAgentRuntimeWithToken(ctx, nsB, arB.Name, tokenA)\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusForbidden, resp.StatusCode)\n    \n    // Cleanup\n    client.DeleteNamespace(ctx, nsA)\n    client.DeleteNamespace(ctx, nsB)\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.6.2 故障恢复 (`integration/failure_recovery_test.go`)\n\n```go\n// TestPodRestartRecovery tests recovery after pod restart\nfunc TestPodRestartRecovery(t *testing.T) {\n    client := setupE2EClient(t)\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    \n    // Create AgentRuntime\n    ar := createEchoAgent(client, \"test-recovery\")\n    client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, ar.Name, 2*time.Minute)\n    \n    // Get pod name\n    podName := getAgentRuntimePodName(client, ar)\n    \n    // Delete pod\n    client.KubeClient().CoreV1().Pods(client.Namespace()).Delete(ctx, podName, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n    \n    // Wait for recovery\n    err := client.WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, ar.Name, 3*time.Minute)\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    \n    // Verify invocation works\n    resp, err := client.InvokeAgent(ctx, ar.Name, map[string]string{\"message\": \"hello\"})\n    require.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, resp.StatusCode)\n}\n```\n\n### 4.7 测试配置\n\n#### 4.7.1 环境变量\n\n| 变量 | 必需 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `E2E_CLUSTER_NAME` | No | `agentcube-e2e` | Kind 集群名称 |\n| `E2E_CLEAN_CLUSTER` | No | `true` | 测试前清理集群 |\n| `E2E_SKIP_SETUP` | No | `false` | 跳过集群设置 |\n| `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | No | `agentcube` | Kubernetes namespace |\n| `AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION` | No | `v0.1.1` | agent-sandbox 版本 |\n| `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT` | No | `8080` | Workload Manager 端口 |\n| `ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT` | No | `8081` | Router 端口 |\n| `REDIS_IMAGE` | No | `redis:7-alpine` | Redis 镜像 |\n| `ARTIFACTS_PATH` | No | `${PWD}/e2e-logs` | 日志输出路径 |\n| `TEST_TIMEOUT` | No | `30m` | 测试超时时间 |\n\n#### 4.7.2 Fixtures 更新\n\n新增 fixtures:\n\n1. `fixtures/agentruntime.yaml`:\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: AgentRuntime\nmetadata:\n  name: test-agentruntime\n  namespace: agentcube\n  labels:\n    agentcube/expose: \"true\"\nspec:\n  image: volcanosh/echo-agent:latest\n  command: [\"python\", \"-m\", \"echo_agent\"]\n  sessionTimeout: \"5m\"\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: \"0.1\"\n      memory: \"64Mi\"\n    limits:\n      cpu: \"0.5\"\n      memory: \"128Mi\"\n```\n\n2. `fixtures/codeinterpreter_warmpool.yaml`:\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: CodeInterpreter\nmetadata:\n  name: test-warmpool-ci\n  namespace: agentcube\nspec:\n  image: volcanosh/picod:latest\n  minIdle: 2\n  maxIdle: 5\n  timeout: \"30s\"\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: \"0.1\"\n      memory: \"64Mi\"\n    limits:\n      cpu: \"1.0\"\n      memory: \"256Mi\"\n```\n\n## 5. Impact Analysis\n\n### 5.1 依赖\n\n| 包 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | Kubernetes client library |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | Kubernetes API types |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | AgentCube 生成的 client-go |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify` | Testing assertions |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | Logging |\n| `gopkg.in/yaml.v3` | YAML parsing for fixtures |\n| `github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2` | BDD testing framework (可选) |\n| `github.com/onsi/gomega` | Ginkgo matcher library (可选) |\n\n### 5.2 受影响组件\n\n1. **Workload Manager**: 被 E2E 测试验证状态同步和生命周期管理\n2. **Router**: 被 E2E 测试验证路由、会话、认证功能\n3. **agent-sandbox-controller**: 被验证 CRD 状态更新和 Pod 管理\n4. **PicoD**: 被验证代码执行和资源限制\n5. **CI/CD Pipeline**: 需要集成 E2E 测试执行\n\n### 5.3 向后兼容性\n\n- E2E 测试是新增功能，不影响现有 API\n- 测试框架设计为可扩展，支持未来新增测试场景\n- 现有 `e2e_test.go` 测试保留并集成到新框架中\n\n### 5.4 风险评估\n\n| 风险 | 可能性 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n|------|--------|------|----------|\n| Kind 集群创建失败 | 低 | 高 | 重试机制、详细日志、备用方案 |\n| 测试 flaky | 中 | 中 | 重试逻辑、超时控制、等待条件 |\n| 资源泄漏 | 中 | 高 | 强制 cleanup、defer 清理、资源配额 |\n| 测试执行时间长 | 高 | 低 | 并行执行、选择性运行、CI 超时配置 |\n| 环境依赖问题 | 低 | 中 | Docker in Docker、预构建镜像 |\n\n## 6. Alternatives Considered\n\n### 6.1 方案 A: 使用真实 Kubernetes 集群（不采用）\n\n**描述**: 在真实 Kubernetes 集群上运行 E2E 测试\n\n**优点**:\n- 最接近生产环境\n- 无 Kind 开销\n\n**缺点**:\n- 需要专用集群\n- 清理困难\n- 成本高\n- 无法快速迭代\n\n**不采用原因**: Kind 提供快速、可重复的测试环境\n\n### 6.2 方案 B: 使用 K3d 而非 Kind（不采用）\n\n**描述**: 使用 K3d 替代 Kind 创建轻量级 Kubernetes 集群\n\n**优点**:\n- 更轻量\n- 启动更快\n\n**缺点**:\n- 社区支持较少\n- 与 Kind API 不完全兼容\n- 文档较少\n\n**不采用原因**: Kind 是 Kubernetes 社区标准，更好的支持和文档\n\n### 6.3 方案 C: 使用 Testinfra 或 Serverspec（不采用）\n\n**描述**: 使用基础设施测试框架\n\n**优点**:\n- 声明式测试语法\n- 支持多种后端\n\n**缺点**:\n- 学习曲线\n- 不适合 Kubernetes 原生测试\n- 社区较小\n\n**不采用原因**: Go 测试框架更成熟，与代码库语言一致\n\n### 6.4 方案 D: 仅使用 HTTP API 测试（部分采用）\n\n**描述**: 仅通过 HTTP API 进行 E2E 测试，不直接操作 K8s API\n\n**优点**:\n- 简单\n- 无需 client-go\n\n**缺点**:\n- 无法验证 CRD 状态\n- 无法测试 informer 机制\n- 覆盖不完整\n\n**采用决策**: 结合两种方法 - 使用 client-go 验证 K8s 资源，使用 HTTP API 验证运行时行为\n\n## 7. Testing Strategy\n\n### 7.1 测试分层\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│         Manual E2E (Full Cluster)       │  ← 完整 E2E 测试套件\n├─────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│      Automated E2E (Kind Cluster)       │  ← CI/CD 运行\n├─────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│    Integration Tests (test/integration) │  ← 组件间集成\n├─────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│       Unit Tests (pkg/*, cmd/*)         │  ← 单元测试\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 7.2 测试执行模式\n\n1. **本地开发**:\n   ```bash\n   make e2e              # 完整 E2E 测试\n   make e2e-fast         # 快速测试（跳过集群重建）\n   make e2e-clean        # 清理集群\n   ```\n\n2. **CI/CD**:\n   ```yaml\n   # GitHub Actions 示例\n   - name: Run E2E Tests\n     run: make e2e\n     env:\n       E2E_CLEAN_CLUSTER: \"true\"\n       TEST_TIMEOUT: \"30m\"\n   ```\n\n3. **选择性运行**:\n   ```bash\n   # 运行特定测试\n   go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run TestAgentRuntime\n   \n   # 跳过某些测试\n   go test -v ./test/e2e/... -skip TestConcurrency\n   ```\n\n### 7.3 覆盖率目标\n\n- **E2E 场景覆盖**: ≥ 90% 关键用户路径\n- **CRD 字段覆盖**: ≥ 80% spec/status 字段\n- **错误场景覆盖**: ≥ 70% 已知错误类型\n- **API 端点覆盖**: 100% 公开 API 端点\n\n### 7.4 测试数据管理\n\n1. **Fixtures as Code**: 所有测试资源使用 Go 代码创建\n2. **Unique Names**: 每个测试使用唯一名称避免冲突\n3. **Cleanup on Exit**: 使用 `defer` 确保资源清理\n4. **Namespace Isolation**: 每个测试套件使用独立 namespace\n\n### 7.5 重试和等待策略\n\n```go\n// 默认重试配置\nvar (\n    DefaultPollInterval = 2 * time.Second\n    DefaultPollTimeout  = 5 * time.Minute\n    DefaultRetries      = 3\n)\n\n// 等待条件满足\nfunc WaitForCondition(ctx context.Context, name string, timeout time.Duration, \n    condition func() (bool, error)) error {\n    \n    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, timeout)\n    defer cancel()\n    \n    for {\n        select {\n        case <-ctx.Done():\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"timeout waiting for %s\", name)\n        default:\n            done, err := condition()\n            if err != nil {\n                return err\n            }\n            if done {\n                return nil\n            }\n            time.Sleep(DefaultPollInterval)\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 8. Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] E2E 测试框架基础结构完成 (`framework/` 包)\n- [ ] AgentRuntime E2E 测试覆盖创建、更新、删除、状态同步\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter E2E 测试覆盖执行流程、暖池、资源限制\n- [ ] Router E2E 测试覆盖健康检查、调用、会话管理、认证\n- [ ] 集成场景测试覆盖多租户、故障恢复\n- [ ] 所有 E2E 测试在 CI/CD 中通过\n- [ ] 测试执行时间 < 30 分钟\n- [ ] 测试 flaky 率 < 5%\n- [ ] 失败时自动收集日志和诊断信息\n- [ ] 测试文档完整（README、示例、故障排除）\n- [ ] 代码覆盖率报告生成\n\n## 9. Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: 测试框架基础 (6h)\n```\n- [ ] 创建 framework/client.go\n- [ ] 创建 framework/wait.go\n- [ ] 创建 framework/fixtures.go\n- [ ] 创建 framework/cleanup.go\n- [ ] 更新 run_e2e.sh 支持新框架\n```\n\n### Phase 2: AgentRuntime E2E 测试 (8h)\n```\n- [ ] 创建 agents/agentruntime_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 agents/agentruntime_status_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 agents/agentruntime_lifecycle_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 agents/agentruntime_routing_test.go\n```\n\n### Phase 3: CodeInterpreter E2E 测试 (10h)\n```\n- [ ] 创建 code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_execution_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_status_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_warmpool_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 code_interpreter/codeinterpreter_limits_test.go\n```\n\n### Phase 4: Router E2E 测试 (6h)\n```\n- [ ] 创建 router/router_health_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 router/router_invoke_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 router/router_session_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 router/router_auth_test.go\n```\n\n### Phase 5: 集成场景测试 (8h)\n```\n- [ ] 创建 integration/multi_tenant_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 integration/failure_recovery_test.go\n- [ ] 创建 integration/concurrency_test.go\n```\n\n### Phase 6: CI/CD 集成和文档 (6h)\n```\n- [ ] 更新 GitHub Actions 配置\n- [ ] 更新 README.md\n- [ ] 添加故障排除指南\n- [ ] 运行完整测试套件验证\n- [ ] 修复 flaky 测试\n```\n\n**总预估时间**: 44 小时\n\n## 10. Success Criteria\n\n1. ✅ 所有 E2E 测试在本地和 CI 环境中稳定通过\n2. ✅ 测试执行时间 < 30 分钟\n3. ✅ 测试 flaky 率 < 5%\n4. ✅ 失败时自动收集详细诊断信息\n5. ✅ 文档完整且易于理解\n6. ✅ 新成员可以运行 E2E 测试无需额外帮助\n7. ✅ 测试覆盖所有关键用户路径\n\n## 11. Dependencies\n\n- Go 1.23+\n- Kind v0.30.0+\n- Helm 3.x\n- Docker\n- Kubernetes v1.31+ (via Kind)\n- agent-sandbox v0.1.1+\n- Redis 7+\n\n## 12. References\n\n- `deployment/client-go.md` - Client-go 生成代码说明\n- `test/e2e/README.md` - 现有 E2E 测试文档\n- `test/e2e/e2e_test.go` - 现有 E2E 测试代码\n- `run_e2e.sh` - E2E 测试运行脚本\n- [Kubernetes Testing Guide](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-testing/testing.md)\n- [client-go testing](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go/tree/master/testing)\n- [Kind documentation](https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go\">\nERROR [27:16] undefined: labels\nERROR [27:37] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [39:44] undefined: labels\nERROR [39:65] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [40:14] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [42:27] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [52:16] undefined: labels\nERROR [52:37] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [53:21] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [61:52] undefined: labels\nERROR [61:73] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [62:14] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [64:27] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [69:57] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [72:15] undefined: errors\nERROR [72:34] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\nERROR [77:15] undefined: runtimev1alpha1\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors de